Answer.Comments:
I found first 8 verb exercises a bit mind-numbing. The routine changed starting w/verb nine and caught me off guard, in terms of screen changes and speed of action(i.e. plus sign.)As such, I found my comprehension slip a bit and had to refocus on the task.

Lastly, my first impression of the exercise was "Oh, this is some template on how better to learn a foreign language." I think that idea may have missed the target.

Thanks for a creative study.

I found first 8 verb exercises a bit mind-numbing. The routine changed starting w/verb nine and caught me off guard, in terms of screen changes and speed of action(i.e. plus sign.)As such, I found my comprehension slip a bit and had to refocus on the task.

Lastly, my first impression of the exercise was "Oh, this is some template on how better to learn a foreign language." I think that idea may have missed the target.

Thanks for a creative study.
